{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1012,"text":"Well, I was born with a rare visual condition"},{"time":4191,"text":"called achromatopsia, which is total color blindness,"},{"time":7904,"text":"so I've never seen color,"},{"time":9774,"text":"and I don't know what color looks like,"},{"time":12297,"text":"because I come from a grayscale world."},{"time":15272,"text":"To me, the sky is always gray,"},{"time":17932,"text":"flowers are always gray,"},{"time":19784,"text":"and television is still in black and white."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21986,"text":"But, since the age of 21,"},{"time":24279,"text":"instead of seeing color, I can hear color."},{"time":28408,"text":"In 2003, I started a project"},{"time":31384,"text":"with computer scientist Adam Montandon,"},{"time":34072,"text":"and the result, with further collaborations"},{"time":37239,"text":"with Peter Kese from Slovenia"},{"time":40087,"text":"and Matias Lizana from Barcelona,"},{"time":42120,"text":"is this electronic eye."},{"time":44485,"text":"It's a color sensor that detects"},{"time":46841,"text":"the color frequency in front of me — (Frequency sounds) —"},{"time":50424,"text":"and sends this frequency to a chip installed"},{"time":52776,"text":"at the back of my head, and I hear the color in front of me"},{"time":55767,"text":"through the bone, through bone conduction."},{"time":58663,"text":"(Frequency sounds) So, for example, if I have, like —"},{"time":65724,"text":"This is the sound of purple. (Frequency sounds)"},{"time":68691,"text":"For example, this is the sound of grass. (Frequency sounds)"},{"time":76109,"text":"This is red, like TED. (Frequency sounds)"},{"time":78234,"text":"This is the sound of a dirty sock. (Laughter)"},{"time":82603,"text":"Which is like yellow, this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84480,"text":"So I've been hearing color all the time for eight years,"},{"time":88537,"text":"since 2004, so I find it completely normal now"},{"time":91172,"text":"to hear color all the time."},{"time":93651,"text":"At the start, though, I had to memorize the names you give"},{"time":98025,"text":"for each color, so I had to memorize the notes,"},{"time":100431,"text":"but after some time, all this information"},{"time":102367,"text":"became a perception."},{"time":104360,"text":"I didn't have to think about the notes."},{"time":106119,"text":"And after some time, this perception became a feeling."},{"time":108744,"text":"I started to have favorite colors,"},{"time":110750,"text":"and I started to dream in colors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112524,"text":"So, when I started to dream in color is when I felt"},{"time":116799,"text":"that the software and my brain had united,"},{"time":119686,"text":"because in my dreams, it was my brain creating"},{"time":122642,"text":"electronic sounds. It wasn't the software,"},{"time":125003,"text":"so that's when I started to feel like a cyborg."},{"time":128522,"text":"It's when I started to feel that the cybernetic device"},{"time":131572,"text":"was no longer a device."},{"time":133762,"text":"It had become a part of my body,"},{"time":136177,"text":"an extension of my senses,"},{"time":138642,"text":"and after some time, it even became a part"},{"time":141268,"text":"of my official image."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144795,"text":"This is my passport from 2004."},{"time":147141,"text":"You're not allowed to appear on U.K. passports"},{"time":150226,"text":"with electronic equipment, but I insisted"},{"time":153038,"text":"to the passport office that what they were seeing"},{"time":155439,"text":"was actually a new part of my body,"},{"time":157943,"text":"an extension of my brain, and they finally accepted me"},{"time":161463,"text":"to appear with the passport photo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163974,"text":"So, life has changed dramatically since I hear color,"},{"time":167431,"text":"because color is almost everywhere,"},{"time":170025,"text":"so the biggest change for example is"},{"time":172902,"text":"going to an art gallery, I can listen to a Picasso,"},{"time":177440,"text":"for example. So it's like I'm going to a concert hall,"},{"time":180294,"text":"because I can listen to the paintings."},{"time":182505,"text":"And supermarkets, I find this is very shocking,"},{"time":184966,"text":"it's very, very attractive to walk along a supermarket."},{"time":187916,"text":"It's like going to a nightclub."},{"time":189404,"text":"It's full of different melodies. (Laughter) Yeah."},{"time":192660,"text":"Especially the aisle with cleaning products."},{"time":194735,"text":"It's just fabulous. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":198086,"text":"Also, the way I dress has changed."},{"time":200558,"text":"Before, I used to dress in a way that it looked good."},{"time":202966,"text":"Now I dress in a way that it sounds good. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207543,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212674,"text":"So today I'm dressed in C major,"},{"time":215183,"text":"so it's quite a happy chord. (Laughter)"},{"time":218492,"text":"If I had to go to a funeral, though,"},{"time":220366,"text":"I would dress in B minor, which would be"},{"time":222933,"text":"turquoise, purple and orange. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":231692,"text":"Also, food, the way I look at food has changed,"},{"time":236037,"text":"because now I can display the food on a plate,"},{"time":239493,"text":"so I can eat my favorite song. (Laughter)"},{"time":242445,"text":"So depending on how I display it,"},{"time":243674,"text":"I can hear and I can compose music with food."},{"time":246424,"text":"So imagine a restaurant where we can have, like,"},{"time":249149,"text":"Lady Gaga salads as starters. (Laughter) I mean,"},{"time":252133,"text":"this would get teenagers to eat their vegetables, probably."},{"time":255150,"text":"And also, some Rachmaninov piano concertos"},{"time":258589,"text":"as main dishes, and some Bjork or Madonna desserts,"},{"time":261823,"text":"that would be a very exciting restaurant"},{"time":264932,"text":"where you can actually eat songs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267692,"text":"Also, the way I perceive beauty has changed,"},{"time":272142,"text":"because when I look at someone, I hear their face,"},{"time":276822,"text":"so someone might look very beautiful but sound terrible."},{"time":281824,"text":"(Laughter) And it might happen the opposite,"},{"time":283585,"text":"the other way around. So I really enjoy creating, like,"},{"time":285833,"text":"sound portraits of people."},{"time":287562,"text":"Instead of drawing someone's face, like drawing the shape,"},{"time":291202,"text":"I point at them with the eye and I write down"},{"time":293633,"text":"the different notes I hear, and then I create sound portraits."},{"time":296904,"text":"Here's some faces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298641,"text":"(Musical chords)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":313168,"text":"Yeah, Nicole Kidman sounds good. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":316601,"text":"Some people, I would never relate, but they sound similar."},{"time":319650,"text":"Prince Charles has some similarities with Nicole Kidman."},{"time":322448,"text":"They have similar sound of eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324585,"text":"So you relate people that you wouldn't relate,"},{"time":326633,"text":"and you can actually also create concerts"},{"time":330146,"text":"by looking at the audience faces."},{"time":332786,"text":"So I connect the eye, and then I play the audience's faces."},{"time":335882,"text":"The good thing about this is,"},{"time":337386,"text":"if the concert doesn't sound good, it's their fault."},{"time":340353,"text":"It's not my fault, because — (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":342624,"text":"And so another thing that happens is that"},{"time":346931,"text":"I started having this secondary effect"},{"time":349808,"text":"that normal sounds started to become color."},{"time":353138,"text":"I heard a telephone tone, and it felt green"},{"time":356899,"text":"because it sounded just like the color green."},{"time":359225,"text":"The BBC beeps, they sound turquoise,"},{"time":362523,"text":"and listening to Mozart became a yellow experience,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":365650,"text":"so I started to paint music and paint people's voices,"},{"time":370410,"text":"because people's voices have frequencies"},{"time":372353,"text":"that I relate to color."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373896,"text":"And here's some music translated into color."},{"time":379015,"text":"For example, Mozart, \"Queen of the Night,\" looks like this."},{"time":384215,"text":"(Music) Very yellow and very colorful,"},{"time":386027,"text":"because there's many different frequencies."},{"time":388217,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":392143,"text":"And this is a completely different song."},{"time":394457,"text":"(Music) It's Justin Bieber's \"Baby.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":398388,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":400119,"text":"It is very pink and very yellow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403689,"text":"So, also voices, I can transform speeches into color,"},{"time":410856,"text":"for example, these are two very well-known speeches."},{"time":414400,"text":"One of them is Martin Luther King's \"I Have A Dream,\""},{"time":418137,"text":"and the other one is Hitler."},{"time":419589,"text":"And I like to exhibit these paintings in the exhibition halls"},{"time":423065,"text":"without labels, and then I ask people,"},{"time":425641,"text":"\"Which one do you prefer?\""},{"time":427488,"text":"And most people change their preference"},{"time":429753,"text":"when I tell them that the one on the left is Hitler"},{"time":432664,"text":"and the one on the right is Martin Luther King."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435784,"text":"So I got to a point when I was able to perceive 360 colors,"},{"time":441523,"text":"just like human vision."},{"time":443108,"text":"I was able to differentiate all the degrees of the color wheel."},{"time":446703,"text":"But then, I just thought that"},{"time":448785,"text":"this human vision wasn't good enough."},{"time":452024,"text":"There's many, many more colors around us"},{"time":454235,"text":"that we cannot perceive,"},{"time":456072,"text":"but that electronic eyes can perceive."},{"time":457828,"text":"So I decided to continue extending my color senses,"},{"time":461557,"text":"and I added infrared and I added ultraviolet"},{"time":465807,"text":"to the color-to-sound scale, so now I can hear colors"},{"time":469165,"text":"that the human eye cannot perceive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471389,"text":"For example, perceiving infrared is good because you can"},{"time":474836,"text":"actually detect if there's movement detectors in a room."},{"time":478904,"text":"I can hear if someone points at me with a remote control."},{"time":482357,"text":"And the good thing about perceiving ultraviolet is that"},{"time":485507,"text":"you can hear if it's a good day or a bad day to sunbathe,"},{"time":490472,"text":"because ultraviolet is a dangerous color,"},{"time":492629,"text":"a color that can actually kill us, so I think we should all have this wish"},{"time":496613,"text":"to perceive things that we cannot perceive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499574,"text":"That's why, two years ago,"},{"time":501309,"text":"I created the Cyborg Foundation,"},{"time":502990,"text":"which is a foundation that tries to help people"},{"time":505432,"text":"become a cyborg, tries to encourage people"},{"time":508129,"text":"to extend their senses"},{"time":509506,"text":"by using technology as part of the body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512577,"text":"We should all think that knowledge comes from our senses,"},{"time":516480,"text":"so if we extend our senses,"},{"time":518456,"text":"we will consequently extend our knowledge."},{"time":521544,"text":"I think life will be much more exciting"},{"time":524337,"text":"when we stop creating applications for mobile phones"},{"time":527561,"text":"and we start creating applications for our own body."},{"time":530962,"text":"I think this will be a big, big change"},{"time":532778,"text":"that we will see during this century."}]},{"cues":[{"time":534856,"text":"So I do encourage you all to think about which senses"},{"time":538771,"text":"you'd like to extend."},{"time":540190,"text":"I would encourage you to become a cyborg."},{"time":543363,"text":"You won't be alone. Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548011,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}